title: Nurses Down Under
overview: Nurses Down Under takes viewers straight to the heart of Sydney's frontline, with exclusive access to the incredible men and women who are working in hospitals across the vibrant Australian city.Â From A&E incidents to operations in theatre, deliveries in maternity wards and the race against time of the organ transplantation team, the UKTV Original series offers an intimate opportunity to see the fascinating world of medicine through the nurses' eyes.
